Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.58,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}任性的Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:26.25,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒映著的雙眼正看著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:42.35,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}吶 漂亮不過是外表逞強而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:47.69,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}對 就連玫瑰也是帶著刺的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:52.86,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我不是那種受傷也無所謂的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:58.70,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}撞到了卻敷衍過去 Pure sign
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:01.57,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}有些地方讓人不耐煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:04.12,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}又有什麼東西就要溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:06.20,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Please don't please wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:09.87,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}我明明想大聲喊出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:11.96,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}任性的Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:16.17,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}倒映著的純情在搖擺不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:20.59,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}另一邊映出的彷彿是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.59,0:01:22.51,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}就算這樣也是Mirror heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:26.39,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比起防守 我的行動更注重進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:29.44,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}比精美的玻璃還要脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:31.23,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}你明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:33.61,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}快注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.77,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}所以強制執行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:40.03,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\be2}希望你能看著一個完整的我
